{"tid":2501412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中大校友】評議會2020週年會員大會：聽日(24號)1400舉行","createTime":"2021-04-23T10:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T11:44:30.000Z","uid":239489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9975c65ab0949d6696525a4210cda1d89470ea","tid":2501412,"uid":239489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"各位中大校友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲記唔記得畀人一拖再拖，又改日期又改地點嘅會員大會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同19立法會一樣，現屆主席由常務委員會通過決定延任最長一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n評議會網站講明原先嘅登記出席截止日期保留適用，即係話之前無報到嘅而家都無得補報番，委任出席投票亦唔可以追加或者換人。但係大家都仲可以做嘅係，幫手提醒身邊嘅中大校友同埋佢哋嘅委任人，<span class=\"red\">記得預留時間出席投票換個真香港人上去，而且唔可以遲到(遲到半個鐘會失去投票權！)，唔好無咗件事！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會議安排<br />\n日期：2021年4月24日（星期六）<br />\n時間：下午2時<br />\n地點及其他安排：紅磡香港體育館<br />\n會議詳情會已經透過電郵通知各位已登記校友及刊登於網頁。<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"https://www.alumni.cuhk.edu.hk/convocation/agm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alumni.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fconvocation%2Fagm%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=19c6b011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.alumni.cuhk.edu.hk/convocation/agm/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">麻煩幫手推同share</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n==============================<br />\n<br />\n舊posts：<br />\n<br />\n[行動post]中大人同我立即登記評議會選民(10/7 deadline)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2099807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2099807</a><br />\n<br />\n救中大，評議會一定要去投票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2090730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2090730</a><br />\n<br />\n[暴大之戰]中文大學校友評議會即將改選，3名年輕民主派區議員參選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072393</a><br />\n<br />\n中大校友評議會2020週年會員大會：目前定於2021/1/9(六)1500舉行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2313197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2313197</a>"},{"pid":"0503dc175857482dcbafa97a938f127b9b6f1437","tid":2501412,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:43:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf72e24f5ccdc391732312cfa932b00558287b85","tid":2501412,"uid":239489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb9975c65ab0949d6696525a4210cda1d89470ea","tid":2501412,"uid":239489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"各位中大校友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲記唔記得畀人一拖再拖，又改日期又改地點嘅會員大會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同19立法會一樣，現屆主席由常務委員會通過決定延任最長一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n評議會網站講明原先嘅登記出席截止日期保留適用，即係話之前無報到嘅而家都無得補報番，委任出席投票亦唔可以追加或者換人。但係大家都仲可以做嘅係，幫手提醒身邊嘅中大校友同埋佢哋嘅委任人，<span class=\"red\">記得預留時間出席投票換個真香港人上去，而且唔可以遲到(遲到半個鐘會失去投票權！)，唔好無咗件事！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會議安排<br />\n日期：2021年4月24日（星期六）<br />\n時間：下午2時<br />\n地點及其他安排：紅磡香港體育館<br />\n會議詳情會已經透過電郵通知各位已登記校友及刊登於網頁。<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"https://www.alumni.cuhk.edu.hk/convocation/agm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alumni.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fconvocation%2Fagm%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=19c6b011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.alumni.cuhk.edu.hk/convocation/